Description: OMARCHY-inspired workflow and aesthetics for COSMIC Desktop
 COSMIC ORDER brings the keyboard-first workflow you love to the desktop
 you deserve. Manage themes, wallpapers, and screensaver settings from a
 single native COSMIC application.
 .
 Features include theme management with live preview, wallpaper browsing
 with thumbnail grid, terminal-based screensaver configuration, power-aware
 effects, caffeine mode to prevent idle sleep, and tool theme sync to
 propagate COSMIC colors to Ghostty and other terminal tools.
